text: Amado Espino III is a Filipino politician from Pangasinan, Philippines. He is currently serving his second term as the Governor of Pangasinan. Espino was first elected Governor in 2016 and was re-elected in 2019. ==References== ==External links== *Province of Pangasinan Official Website Category:Living people Category:Governors of Pangasinan Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:1977 births
